        Parameters:
        args -
        m0 - = total weight of rocket (kg)
        mW - = intital amount of water (liters)
        vB - = bottdle volume (liters)
        p0 - = intial air pressure (pascals)
        cD - = drag coefficient ( no unit)
        step - = time step
        rBot - = bottle radius (m)
        rNoz - = nozzle radius (m)
        iP - = internal pressure (pascals)
        pW - = water density
        oP - = external pressure
        m - = mass at a given time
        a - = acceleration at a given time
        v - = velocity at a given time
        h - = height at a given time
        pA - = air density at a given time general notes: p + letter = density, letter + p = pressure ex: pA = air density, iP = internal pressure
